starvationevasion.common.messages

Class Goodbye

  • java.lang.Object
    • starvationevasion.common.messages.Goodbye
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Goodbye
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Shea Polansky Sent by the server to the client when it is disconnecting the client, or from the client to the server for the same reason. If the client is sending the message, the proscribed reason is "User disconnect", if the user has chosen to disconnect. In the case of send/receive errors, or other reasons not relating to "the user wanted to leave", other messages may be sent.
